'''Longitudinal data system''' is a [[data system]] capable of [[Tracking system|tracking]] [[student]] information over multiple years in multiple [[school]]s.  The term appears in [[Federal law|Federal]] [[law of the United States]] to describe such a system.  [[Administration of federal assistance in the United States|Federal funding]] is provided to aid the design and implementation of such systems.

